"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-culture-culture-news-shacarri-richardson-olympics-grandmother-vogue-interview-1235056085\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByMankaprr Conteh  As her star has risen as theworld's fastest woman,Sha'Carri Richardsonhas always honored her roots.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AsVogue's cover star ahead of the ParisOlympics, she included some of her family - her sister, an aunt, and several cousins - in her photo shoot.\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next-best known member of Richardson's family may be her grandmother Betty Harp, who she affectionately calls \\\"Big Momma\\\" and is the person who raised her.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999943829607, \"rank\": 5.616755748956192e-09, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\", \"score\": 0.998522818413745, \"rank\": 0.0014793662952187338, \"text\": \"Betty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After both of Richardson's Olympic-qualifying runs in 2021 and earlier this year, she ran to the stands and into Harp's arms.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999943829607, \"rank\": 5.616755748956192e-09, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the new interview withVogue, Harp discussed how her own strength has empowered Richardson.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999943829607, \"rank\": 5.616755748956192e-09, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sha'Carri's tough; I made her tough,\\\" Harp said.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a strong woman, I have overcome obstacles in my life.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I knew what I was talking about when, from time to time, things got hard and she'd want to quit - and I'd say, 'Do not start nothing and do not finish it.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You start, you finish.\\\"\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson bolstered Harp's words.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999943829607, \"rank\": 5.616755748956192e-09, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything I am, it's because of that strong, wise Black woman,\\\" she said about her grandmother.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, I have been blessed, because I have had other people in my life who have helped me along.\